📁 Project Overview
This project focuses on understanding sales patterns, product performance, and customer behavior to help make data-driven business decisions. It includes:

Data Cleaning & Transformation
Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
Visualizations with Matplotlib and Seaborn
Insights and Recommendations

🛠Libraries
Pandas – Data manipulation and analysis
NumPy – Numerical computing
Matplotlib & Seaborn – Data visualization
Jupyter Notebook – Interactive development

📌 Key Insights
✔️ Identified top-selling products and categories
✔️ Analyzed daily and monthly sales trends
✔️ Determined peak hours for order volume
✔️ Examined customer order frequency and repeat behavior
✔️ Suggested improvements for product placement and inventory
